  <p>Content Publisher is in private beta and supports most of the features that are available on Whitehall.</p>
  <p>With this form you can tell us more about your experience with the new app so we can make it better. If youâ€™re having issues publishing or editing a document raise a <a class="link-inherit" href="<%= new_technical_fault_report_path %>">support request</a> so you can get technical help.</p>
